models

Class MultiMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.MultiMap<K,V>

  • public class MultiMap<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
    A strand of the HashMap data structure where the value is a Collection of items and both key and value types are received from the type parameters. The first parameter refer to the type of the MultiMap keys. The second parameter refer to the type of the Collection items.
